            "I highly recommend Akanksha Opticals for everyone.",
            "Truly the best optical store in the Wagholi area.",
            "Excellent customer service from start to finish.",
            "Got my new glasses delivered today, very happy.",
            "A very reliable shop for all eyewear needs.",
            "The staff here is very polite and helpful.",
            "Came here for an eye test and new spectacles.",
            "Found this shop via Google Reviews and it lived up to the hype.",
            "Such a wide range of frames available here.",
            "Quality service at very reasonable prices.",
            "They treat every customer with great care.",
            "I broke my glasses and they fixed it quickly.",
            "Needed blue cut lenses for office work, got the best deal here.",
            "My family has been visiting this shop for years.",
            "Very hygienic and well-maintained store.",
            "The owner is very knowledgeable and guided me well.",
            "Superb experience getting my contact lenses here.",
            "Quick, efficient, and affordable service.",
            "I love the collection of designer frames they have.",
            "Accurate eye testing and perfect fitting glasses.",
            "They understand customer needs very well.",
            "Definitely the top-rated optician in Wagholi.",
            "Smooth and hassle-free process.",
            "Great value for money products.",
            "Friendly atmosphere and professional attitude.",
            "I am fully satisfied with my purchase.",
            "Top notch quality lenses provided.",
            "They have the latest trendy glasses.",
            "My search for the perfect glasses ended here.",
            "Wonderful experience!",
            "Thank you Akanksha Opticals for the great service."
        ],

        // Keyword Specific Sentences
        keywords: {
            "Best Store": ["Hands down the best optical store in Wagholi.", "Easily the finest shop for eyewear in the area.", "No other store matches their quality service.", "This is the best optical shop I've found nearby.", "The overall vibe and service make it the best store."],
            "Best Optician": ["The optician is very experienced and skilled.", "Best optician I have consulted so far.", "He explains everything about eye health clearly.", "Very patient and accurate optician.", "Trustworthy advice from the optician."],
            "Staff": ["The staff is extremely professional and polite.", "Loved how the staff helped me choose the frame.", "Very courteous staff members.", "The team is efficient and friendly.", "Staff behavior is 10/10."],
